examples.content:
Here's a simple demo script:

```javascript
var comp = app.project.activeItem;
if (comp && comp instanceof CompItem) {
  app.beginUndoGroup('Batch Set Opacity Keyframes');
  for (var i = 1; i <= comp.numLayers; i++) {
    var layer = comp.layer(i);
    var opacity = layer.property('Opacity');
    opacity.setValueAtTime(0, 0);
    opacity.setValueAtTime(10 / comp.frameRate, 100);
  }
  app.endUndoGroup();
} else {
  alert('Please select a composition first');
}
```

You can copy and paste this into AE's script editor to run. It will make all layers' opacity increase from 0 to 100 over 10 frames. Would you like me to further optimize or add features?
